Package org.cloudgraph.mapreduce

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphAccessor
    Supports access to arbitrary data graphs at various stages of a Job as supplied based on the given query.
    GraphMutator
    Supports tracking and commit of modifications to arbitrary data graphs at various stages of a Job.
    GraphService
    Supports access, tracking and commit of modifications to arbitrary data graphs at various stages of a Job.
    GraphXml  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Counters  
    GraphWritable
    Allows data graphs to be consumable by Hadoop using XML serialization under standard SDO provided mechanisms.
    GraphXmlInputFormat
    An XML oriented input format based on FileInputFormat
    GraphXmlMapper<KEYOUT,VALUEOUT>
    Supplies fully realized data graphs as the input value to MapReduce Mapper client subclasses, the input key being an offset into the processed file and the value being a GraphWritable assembled from a single SDO graph XML line read from the file.
    GraphXmlOutputFormat
    An XML oriented output format based on FileOutputFormat
    GraphXmlRecordReader
    An HDFS XML text file record reader that iterates over HDFS data for the current TableSplit, unmarshalling the XML as structured data graphs based on structural and XML-specific metadata from the underlying domain model.
    GraphXmlRecordWriter
